dmca.title: Blog Post DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
Hi I had made a post along with replies on usenet. The infringing website made a verbatim copy of the posts on their website forum without authorization. The website does not provide contact information, and I want the urls removed from search results.

The post begins with:

"Hello I'm a first time poster. I think I may have something that might help some of you, but I'm not sure if it fits IBS, so just read on."

The alias clearly identifies me as the author.

The original authorized work was on usenet and is no longer available.
